Subject: Offline Temporary Password for Computer is not working
Description:
We can generate offline temporary password for a computer; however, an error is returned to the client when the OTP is entered to try and use:
"Invalid Authorization Code"
Creating OTP for a user is working as expected.
I have print screens, but the option to attach a file is grayed out and I am not able to attach.
What_We_Know__c:
OTP is not working when selecting it for a computer, but it does for user
this is a known bug
found the server patch that fixes this - MP-HWA-EPP4-U0066-M0001
Next_Steps__c: waiting on the customer to schedule a remote session to apply the server patch
Solution_Comment__c: We have applied the  MP-HWA-EPP4-U0066-M0001 Offline Patch to the EPP server and were able to download the latest EPP Client(6.2.4.2) that contains the fix for the OTP issue.
